{"title":"外国谚语  （文明礼貌）","authors":["王连义　辛智有"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":3,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"外国谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（文明礼貌）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要人尊敬你，你先尊敬人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（朝鲜）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人美在心不在貌（朝鲜）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄金买不到好名声（缅甸）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"负债可偿还，丧德不可复"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（印度）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁可无钱，不可无耻（英国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁肯丧失性命，不要失掉名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誉（土耳其）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名声扫地生犹死（西班牙）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恶行结不出善果，污水当不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了镜子（意大利）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲究卫生是美德（英国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遵守秩序最有礼（法国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公开认错心灵美（英国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好言好语事事通（美国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽广的河流平静，有教养的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人谦逊（蒙古）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骂人是不讲道理的人的道理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（法国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯腰帮助孩子的人形象最高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（美国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父母的美德是子女最大的财"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富（法国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得人心者永生（非洲）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王连义　辛智有辑译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}